Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Admin
    Represent the admin who control and give permissions to playgrounds Class Admin inherits from class User
    List
    Class List works like a data base for the program It stores all information of players, owners, playgrounds and requests and return them if needed
    Main
    Main class to run the program
    Owner
    Class Owner to represent the Playground owner Class Owner inherits from class User
    Player
    Class Player controls of all players and their books and requests
    Playground
    Class Playground controls of all playground and their available timeslots
    Request
    Class Request to control requests between two classes
    TimeSlot
    Timeslot class to hold the time slot of the playground and has attribute taken to know if the slot is booked or not using 24 hours format 00:00
    User
    Class User represent the users data User can be Player, Playground owner or Admin
    WelcomeScreen
    WelcomeScreen class to start the program and return to welcome screen if needed
